texts.Description:PermissionCacheType: Permission-related cache is stored in sessionStorage or localStorage
texts.Description:ShowSettingButton: Whether to show the configuration button
texts.Description:ShowDarkModeToggle: Whether to show the theme switch button
texts.Description:GrayMode: Website gray mode, open for possible mourning dates
texts.Description:FullContent: Whether to cancel the menu, the top, the multi-tab page display, for possible embedded in other systems
texts.Description:OpenKeepAlive: Whether to enable KeepAlive cache is best to close during development, otherwise the cache needs to be cleared every time
texts.Description:LockTime: Automatic screen lock time, 0 does not lock the screen. Unit minute default 0
texts.Description:ShowBreadCrumbIcon: Whether to show the breadcrumb icon
texts.Description:UseOpenBackTop: Whether to open back to top
texts.Description:CanEmbedIFramePage: Is it possible to embed iframe pages
texts.Description:CloseMessageOnSwitch: Whether to delete unclosed messages and notify when switching the interface
texts.Description:RemoveAllHttpPending: Whether to cancel the http request that has been sent but not responded when switching the interface.
texts.Description:Header_ShowFullScreen: Whether to show the full screen button
texts.Description:Header_UseLockPage: Whether to enable the lock screen function
texts.Description:Header_ShowDoc: Whether to show the document button
texts.Description:Header_ShowNotice: Whether to show the notification button
texts.Description:Header_ShowSearch: Whether to display the menu search
texts.Description:Menu_Fixed: Whether to fix the left menu
texts.Description:Menu_Accordion: Turn on accordion mode, only show a menu
texts.Description:Menu_CollapsedShowTitle: Whether to display the menu name when folding the menu
texts.Description:MultiTabs_CanDrag: Is it possible to drag and drop sorting tabs
texts.Description:MultiTabs_ShowRedo: Whether to show the refresh button
texts.Description:MultiTabs_ShowFold: Whether to show the collapse button
texts.Description:Transition_OpenPageLoading: Whether to open page switching loading
texts.Description:Transition_OpenNProgress: Whether to open the top progress bar
texts.Description:BeforeMini_MenuCollapsed: Restores the shrunken menu when restoring the window
texts.Description:BeforeMini_MenuSplit: Restore separated menus when restoring Windows
texts.Description:BeforeMini_MenuMode: Restore menu mode when restore window
texts.Description:BeforeMini_MenuType: Restore menu type when restore window
